snippet.title: Super Sketch Bob - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Sketch Bob is a 2D action platformer which gives you the power to draw ladders, bridges and trampolines to overcome challenges and save the day! Draw platforming objects in real-time as you solve puzzles, find hidden secrets, and traverse six action-packed worlds!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/497870/Super_Sketch_Bob/
